  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_01_04: Yose ben Yoezer (a man) of Zeredah and Yose ben Yohanan (a man) of Jerusalem ...",
  "body": "Yose ben Yoezer (a man) of Zeredah and Yose ben Yohanan (a man) of Jerusalem received [the oral tradition] from them [i.e. Shimon the Righteous and Antigonus]. Yose ben Yoezer used to say: let thy house be a house of meeting for the Sages and sit in the very dust of their feet, and drink in their words with thirst.",
